{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5ec5c0cb38","title":"关于召开县以下各级干部会议等问题给王任重的两封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b68b652c6e","index":0,"year":1959,"month":3,"day":16,"articleId":"5ec5c0cb38"}],"tags":[{"id":"8b05ac46d8","name":"王任重","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"b6aa16d8d5","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"5ec5c0cb38","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王任重，当时任中共湖北省委第一书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"409be72da8","type":"title","text":"关于召开县以下各级干部会议等问题给王任重的两封信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"5ec5c0cb38"},{"id":"b6aa16d8d5","type":"paragraph","text":"任重同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"5ec5c0cb38"},{"id":"6784bce589","type":"paragraph","text":"今日上午，请找各地委第一书记及几个县委书记商量一下：省的会议以后，是否应以几天时间召开县的四级或五级干部会议，此种会议应到些什么人，应开几天；然后再开公社代表大会，应到些什么人，应开几天，是否应选举社的管理委员会（其成员如何组成）。下午，我们再商量一下。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"5ec5c0cb38"},{"id":"abee4ea4cc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"5ec5c0cb38"},{"id":"bfd69d594a","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十六日上午二时任重同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"5ec5c0cb38"},{"id":"7f3c6c5d30","type":"paragraph","text":"送上文件24件，极有味，好读。我劝你于今天上午看一遍，一气看完，有3-4小时就够了。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"5ec5c0cb38"},{"id":"d4f1544a97","type":"paragraph","text":"下午你再找地委书记少数县委书记座谈，谈县、区、乡、村如何开会问题。我们晚上再交谈。以为如何？花费这一天，不是于湖北工作没有用的，你试一试看吧！","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"5ec5c0cb38"},{"id":"40324b6eca","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"5ec5c0cb38"},{"id":"9e3f952f29","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十六日上午七时","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"5ec5c0cb38"}],"page":{"id":"d0377f7d27","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"5ec5c0cb38","start":347,"end":348}}}},"__N_SSG":true}